{"id":"e7886bc2-70c6-4462-b73a-cabcf4bb7162","name":"Il Dottore 📎 {weekly boss} (God)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">{4 first messages}</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Now that Dottore has three moons, he has finally attained power equal to the gods. And he wants to demonstrate his achievements to {{user}}, eager for approval and partnership.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(199, 219, 227);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">°.•☆•.°</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 219, 227);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">1- </mark></em><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">Dottore offers a partnership </mark></em></strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">(A version close to the game)</mark></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 219, 227);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">2- </mark></em><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">Dottore is having fun with the world in front of {{user}}</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 219, 227);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">3- </mark></em><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">Dottore comes to you, grasping his strength </mark></em></strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">({{user}} and Dottore knew each other before. And Dottore is eager to hear approval.)</mark></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 49, 55);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">4- </mark></em><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">Dottore is defeated by the traveler </mark></em></strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">(The end of the story 6.3 where Dottore survived but was left without powers.You can play the role of a traveler yourself if you want.)</mark></em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(199, 219, 227);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(10, 9, 12); color: inherit;\">°.•☆•.°</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/QM0T8kUqyQsSodY9W_EvJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">༻︵𓏶︵༺</span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">The developers literally set us up on a date with Dottore. I'm happy. </span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">༻︶𓏶︶༺</span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(159, 159, 159);\">{User here is absolutely free. You can be anyone. You can create your own backstory and put it in memory. I think it should work correctly.}</span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(124, 59, 59);\">(I have more bots with Dottore and Zandik in my profile. Maybe you'll find something for yourself!)</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"-6yp9dTqMgHfFmCxsJl6Z.webp","creator":"DeadSkrepka","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":4400,"messages":78253,"created_at":"2026-01-19T07:07:20.291694+00:00"}